===Trying to enter the Training Grounds with a follower===
* {{tbox|Followers are not allowed in the Knight Waves. You'll need to put it away if you wish to enter.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Upon completing the Knight Waves===
* '''Merlin:''' Well done, young adventurer. You truly are a worthy knight.
* {{tbox|You receive access to the prayers Chivalry and Piety and 20,000 XP in your Hitpoints, Strength, Attack, and Defence skills. You may also speak to Merlin to set your respawn point to Camelot.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Merlin near the training grounds===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Merlin:''' Excuse me for rushing off like this, but I must get back to my workroom.
* {{qact|Merlin disappears.}}
* {{tact|end}}
